Mentions

Users

If you want mention a user you can use the @ tag wich automatically creates an hyperlink to the users profile.

Hi @System how are you?

Pages

If you want link to a specific page you can use the & tag wich automatically creates an hyperlink to the specific page.

look at the &home page

Hyperlinks

Urls are automatically converted into hyperlinks. If your url points to an video or image Amun tries in some cases to discover informations about the media item and appends a preview to your post.

look at this video http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4EL67mjv1nM ;D

Formatting content

Amun uses a subset of the markdown syntax to provide an easy way to format content. Please use the following formatting rules in your content so that readers can enjoy reading your content. Note the markdown syntax is only to simplify creating content without writing html if you prefer you can also write plain html.

Paragraphs

Here an example how text will be converted into paragraphs. Note if you have two trailing spaces at a line a <br /> tag will be inserted.

Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr

sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et.
At vero eos et accusam et justo duo dolores

invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam  
sed diam voluptua

<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr </p>
<p>sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et. At vero eos et accusam et justo duo dolores </p>
<p>invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam<br />sed diam voluptua </p>

Code

Indent four spaces or one tab to create an escaped <pre> block. The text will be wrapped in tags, and displayed in a monospaced font. The first four spaces will be stripped off, but all other whitespace will be preserved. Markdown and HTML is ignored within a code block

    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        System.out.println("Hello World !!!");
    }

<pre class="prettyprint">
public static void main(String args[])
{
	System.out.println("Hello World !!!");
}
</pre>

Quotes

Add a > to the beginning of any line to create a <blockquote>.

> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
> consetetur sadipscing elitr
> sed diam nonumy eirmod

tempor invidunt ut labore

<blockquote>
	<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consetetur sadipscing elitr sed diam nonumy eirmod </p>
</blockquote>
<p>tempor invidunt ut labore </p>

Lists

A bulleted <ul> list:

* Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet

* tempor invidunt ut labore

	<li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</li>

	<li>tempor invidunt ut labore</li>
</ul>

Restrictions

Note all the formating capabilities depends on the html tags wich are allowed for your user group. Website administrators can insert any kind of html tags where anonymous user can use only a small subset inorder to prevent misuse.
